x
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[1] 1 2 3
```


:::

```{.r .cell-code}
typeof(x)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[1] "integer"
```


:::
:::

:::

::: {.column .fragment width="35%"}

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
y <- as.character(x)
y
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[1] "1" "2" "3"
```


:::

```{.r .cell-code}
typeof(y)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[1] "character"
```


:::
:::

:::
:::

## Converting between types

::: hand
with intention...
:::

::: columns
::: {.column width="35%"}

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
x <- c(TRUE, FALSE)
x
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[1]  TRUE FALSE
```


:::

```{.r .cell-code}
typeof(x)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[1] "logical"
```


:::
:::

:::

::: {.column .fragment width="35%"}

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
y <- as.numeric(x)
y
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[1] 1 0
```


:::

```{.r .cell-code}
typeof(y)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
